sentence: The following companies are expected to report earnings prior to market open on 10/23/2015.
Visit our Earnings Calendar for a full list of expected earnings releases.
Procter & Gamble Company ( PG ) is reporting for the quarter ending September 30, 2015.
The cleaning company's consensus earnings per share forecast from the 10 analysts that follow the stock is $0.94.
This value represents a 12.15% decrease compared to the same quarter last year.
PG missed the consensus earnings per share in the 3rd calendar quarter of 2014 by -0.93%.
Zacks Investment Research reports that the 2016 Price to Earnings ratio for PG is 19.42 vs. an industry ratio of 20.30.
